{"id":1175,"date":"2021-02-16T21:51:31","date_gmt":"2021-02-16T16:21:31","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost?page_id=1175"},"modified":"2023-11-06T23:21:49","modified_gmt":"2023-11-06T17:51:49","slug":"po","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/localhost\/?page_id=1175","title":{"rendered":"Photo Restoration and Colorization"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-100 has-custom-font-size is-style-outline has-small-font-size\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-foreground-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/\" style=\"border-radius:100px;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">Homepage<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Restoring and colorizing vintage Indian photos is an endeavor I have loved the most, but it requires significant effort as rarely anyone else is taking on this important task. I have tried many approaches to obtain the original high-resolution photos needed to do quality work. This has involved contacting libraries and museums to find prints in their collections. However, most photos available online are too low-resolution to work with effectively. Sometimes I was successful in acquiring an original, other times I had to upscale lower-quality images using software like Topaz to make them suitable for editing. The editing process in Photoshop is extensive. It involves carefully removing scratches, dust, tears and other damage, which sometimes requires reconstructing parts that were too far gone. Lighting, shadows and contrast must be corrected to improve the visual quality. Colorization is especially labor-intensive, requiring research to determine accurate historic colors. Layers upon layers are built up as each element is meticulously colored to be as true to the original as possible, despite the inherent limitations. While the colors can never be perfectly reproduced, striving for accuracy honors the history captured in these photos. Here all are downscaled to less than 1000-pixel height and width.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"688\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2701\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-2.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-2-300x206.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-2-150x103.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-2-768x528.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-2-500x344.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-2-800x550.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"688\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2702\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-1.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-1-300x206.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-1-150x103.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-1-768x528.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-1-500x344.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-1-800x550.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 1943, Burma, WWII, An Indian infantry section of the 2nd Battalion, 7th Rajput Regiment on the Arakan front during Japanese Invasion.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"716\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2703\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-2.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-2-300x215.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-2-150x107.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-2-768x550.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-2-500x358.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-2-800x573.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"716\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2705\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-1.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-1-300x215.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-1-150x107.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-1-768x550.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-1-500x358.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-1-800x573.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 1943, Italy, WWII, A scout car crew of 6th Duke of Connaught\u2019s Own Lancers, Indian Armored Corps, chat with youngsters in San Felice, Italy, during the advance towards the river Sangro against the Germans.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"819\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2706\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-2-2.jpg 819w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-2-2-246x300.jpg 246w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-2-2-123x150.jpg 123w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-2-2-768x938.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-2-2-500x611.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-2-2-800x977.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 819px) 100vw, 819px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"819\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2704\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-4.jpg 819w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-4-246x300.jpg 246w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-4-123x150.jpg 123w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-4-768x938.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-4-500x611.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-4-800x977.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 819px) 100vw, 819px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 1949, USA, Indian Prime Minister Jawaharlal Nehru visit Albert Einstein at the&nbsp;Albert Einstein House&nbsp;at 112 Mercer Street in Princeton.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"698\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2708\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-2-2.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-2-2-300x209.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-2-2-150x105.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-2-2-768x536.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-2-2-500x349.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-2-2-800x558.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"698\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2707\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-4.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-4-300x209.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-4-150x105.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-4-768x536.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-4-500x349.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-4-800x558.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 1951, Korea, Korean War, A medic from Indian Army clenches his hands, indicating the intense pain in his leg which has been almost completely blown off by a bomb.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"701\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2709\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5-2-2.jpg 701w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5-2-2-210x300.jpg 210w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5-2-2-105x150.jpg 105w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5-2-2-500x713.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 701px) 100vw, 701px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"701\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2710\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5-4.jpg 701w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5-4-210x300.jpg 210w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5-4-105x150.jpg 105w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5-4-500x713.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 701px) 100vw, 701px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 3 June 1945, Britain, Chief Officer Margaret L Cooper, Deputy Director of the Women\u2019s Royal Indian Naval Service (WRINS), with Second Officer Kalyani Sen, WRINS at Rosyth.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"997\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2712\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-2.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-2-300x300.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-2-768x766.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-2-500x499.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-2-800x798.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"996\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2711\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-1.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-1-768x765.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-1-500x498.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-1-800x797.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 21 June 1941, Egypt, WWII, Soldiers of the 4th Indian Division scrawl a lorry \u201cKhyber Pass to Hellfire Pass\u201d during Operation Battle Axe.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"723\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2713\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-2.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-2-300x217.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-2-150x108.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-2-768x555.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-2-500x362.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-2-800x578.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"723\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2714\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-1.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-1-300x217.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-1-150x108.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-1-768x555.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-1-500x362.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-1-800x578.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 1932, India, Sarla Thakral, the first Indian woman pilot.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"824\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2715\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-2.jpg 824w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-2-247x300.jpg 247w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-2-124x150.jpg 124w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-2-768x932.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-2-500x607.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-2-800x971.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 824px) 100vw, 824px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"824\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2716\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-1.jpg 824w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-1-247x300.jpg 247w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-1-124x150.jpg 124w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-1-768x932.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-1-500x607.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-1-800x971.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 824px) 100vw, 824px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 1940, India, Mahatma Gandhi studying leprosy germs at Sevagram Ashram.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"568\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2717\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-2.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-2-300x170.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-2-150x85.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-2-768x436.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-2-500x284.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-2-800x454.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"568\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2718\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-1.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-1-300x170.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-1-150x85.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-1-768x436.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-1-500x284.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-1-800x454.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 11 December 1946, India, First day of Constituent Assembly of India. In the first row (From Left):&nbsp;Dr. B. R. Ambedkar,&nbsp;B. G. Kher,&nbsp;Vallabhai Patel&nbsp;and&nbsp;K. M. Munshi.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"840\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2719\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-2-2.jpg 840w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-2-2-252x300.jpg 252w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-2-2-126x150.jpg 126w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-2-2-768x914.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-2-2-500x595.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-2-2-800x952.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"840\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2720\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-5.jpg 840w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-5-252x300.jpg 252w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-5-126x150.jpg 126w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-5-768x914.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-5-500x595.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-5-800x952.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 1860s, India, Portrait of a man of the Kochh Mandai tribe holding a thick-bladed agricultural knife, eastern Bengal.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"731\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2721\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-2-2.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-2-2-300x219.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-2-2-150x110.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-2-2-768x561.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-2-2-500x366.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-2-2-800x585.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"731\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2722\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-4.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-4-300x219.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-4-150x110.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-4-768x561.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-4-500x366.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-4-800x585.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 1914, France, WWII, Indian Soldiers from Sikh regiment arrive, being welcomed by locals with flowers.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"731\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2723\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-2.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-2-300x219.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-2-150x110.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-2-768x561.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-2-500x366.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-2-800x585.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"731\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2724\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-1.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-1-300x219.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-1-150x110.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-1-768x561.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-1-500x366.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-1-800x585.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 1870s, India, A tribal family from central province.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"645\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/14-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2727\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/14-2-2.jpg 645w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/14-2-2-194x300.jpg 194w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/14-2-2-97x150.jpg 97w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/14-2-2-500x775.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 645px) 100vw, 645px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"604\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/14-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2728\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/14-5.jpg 604w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/14-5-181x300.jpg 181w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/14-5-91x150.jpg 91w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/14-5-500x828.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 604px) 100vw, 604px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 1976, India, Portrait of a friend.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"776\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2729\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-2-2.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-2-2-300x233.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-2-2-150x116.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-2-2-768x596.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-2-2-500x388.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-2-2-800x621.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"765\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2730\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-7.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-7-300x230.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-7-150x115.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-7-768x588.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-7-500x383.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-7-800x612.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 1950s, India, Portrait of a friend.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"703\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/13-2-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2725\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/13-2-1.jpg 703w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/13-2-1-211x300.jpg 211w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/13-2-1-105x150.jpg 105w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/13-2-1-500x711.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 703px) 100vw, 703px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"230\" height=\"331\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/13-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2761\" style=\"width:710px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/13-4.jpg 230w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/13-4-208x300.jpg 208w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/13-4-104x150.jpg 104w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 230px) 100vw, 230px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 1986, India, Portrait.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"847\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2731\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-2.jpg 847w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-2-254x300.jpg 254w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-2-127x150.jpg 127w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-2-768x907.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-2-500x590.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-2-800x945.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 847px) 100vw, 847px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"844\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2732\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-1.jpg 844w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-1-253x300.jpg 253w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-1-127x150.jpg 127w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-1-768x910.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-1-500x592.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-1-800x948.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 844px) 100vw, 844px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 1978, India, Old passport photos.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"686\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17-2-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2733\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17-2-4.jpg 686w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17-2-4-206x300.jpg 206w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17-2-4-103x150.jpg 103w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17-2-4-500x729.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 686px) 100vw, 686px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Colorized.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"626\" height=\"922\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2734\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17.png 626w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17-204x300.png 204w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17-102x150.png 102w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17-500x736.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Original: 1978, India, Old passport photos.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Restoring and colorizing vintage Indian photos is an endeavor I have loved the most, but it requires significant effort as rarely anyone else is taking on this important task. I have tried many approaches to obtain the original high-resolution photos needed to do quality work. This has involved contacting libraries and museums to find prints<a class=\"more-link\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/?page_id=1175\">Continue reading <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">&#8220;Photo Restoration and Colorization&#8221;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":198642521,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_coblocks_attr":"","_coblocks_dimensions":"","_coblocks_responsive_height":"","_coblocks_accordion_ie_support":"","footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1175"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/users\/198642521"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcomments&post=1175"}],"version-history":[{"count":124,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1175\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3060,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/ind